title: The Salvation Army North Boroughs Worship & Service Center hosting Dance for the World 
description: PITTSBURGH &mdash; The Salvation Army North Boroughs Worship and Service Center is hosting a &ldquo;Dance for the World&rdquo; fundraiser and pow wow, bringing the community together for a cultural celebration of unity. The event will take place Saturday, September 11 from 10 a. m. to 6 p. m. at the Borough of Avalon Park, 708 New Brighton Road, Avalon, PA. This event is FREE, and families are encouraged to RSVP at www. salvationarmywpa.
